title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Solve The Data Leaks to Earn 2X GTA$ and RP
content:
Help Franklin solve the case of Dr. Dre’s stolen cell phone and take down those responsible in The Data Leaks to earn 2X GTA$ and RP. Plus, deliver the culprit behind the phone robbery to Dre in The Contract’s finale for the GTA$100,000 Weekly Challenge bonus.

Join the world of high-profile problem-solving by heading over to Dynasty 8 Executive and purchasing your own Agency this week, with 30% off Agency Properties and their upgrades and modifications.
